oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Songwriters Association International's Legislative Show (Feb. 2009)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluebird Café (Restaurant : Nashville, Tenn.); Fund raising; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color lobby card (purple and brown on white) announcing Nashville Songwriters Association International's Legislative Show with David Lee, Wynn Varble, Tony Lane, and George Teren at the Bluebird Cafe on February 12. Proceeds from the event go towards NSAI's Legislative efforts, which support the rights of songwriters everywhere. Poster features woodcuts of stars.
